Executive Director, Finance and Administration of the Niger Delta Development Commission (NDDC) Dr. Christian Oyirinda Amadi has become a fellow of the Institute of Corporate Administration of Nigeria. A letter by Mrs. Joy Samuel of the institute’s secretariat said the award was in recognition of Amadi’s dedication and commitment to service, upward mobile and visionary approach to administrative matters, and professionalism in service delivery. The investiture, she added, has been bestowed on the recipient based on his meteoric rise in financial matters, undiluted love for the development of the Niger Delta and his cosmopolitan approach to managerial issues.